{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/pixel-2-review-and-why-Nexus-6p-is-a-bad-choice","result":{"data":{"post":{"html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1080px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fbcc396c08462bc49a1500e3c1c02b17/243ce/pixel.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Pixel 2 shot\"\n        title=\"Pixel 2 shot\"\n        src=\"/static/fbcc396c08462bc49a1500e3c1c02b17/b4133/pixel.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fbcc396c08462bc49a1500e3c1c02b17/d5225/pixel.jpg 270w,\n/static/fbcc396c08462bc49a1500e3c1c02b17/3c312/pixel.jpg 540w,\n/static/fbcc396c08462bc49a1500e3c1c02b17/b4133/pixel.jpg 1080w,\n/static/fbcc396c08462bc49a1500e3c1c02b17/266b5/pixel.jpg 1620w,\n/static/fbcc396c08462bc49a1500e3c1c02b17/0bf41/pixel.jpg 2160w,\n/static/fbcc396c08462bc49a1500e3c1c02b17/243ce/pixel.jpg 4032w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Iâ€™ve been using the Nexus 6p for 2 years until recently as I had to upgrade to the <a href=\"https://amzn.to/2NX1JXq\">Google Pixel 2</a> for various reasons which are really frustrating to a level that I highly donâ€™t recommend buying the Nexus 6p.</p>\n<p>Iâ€™ll walk you through the pros &#x26; cons of the Nexus 6p real quick before I move on to the Pixel 2.</p>\n<h2 id=\"camera\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#camera\" aria-label=\"camera permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Camera</h2>\n<p>Nexus 6p has a really good camera with the Google camera app built in that shots some great pictures combined with HDR, your photos will look amazing (see <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@smakosh\">examples</a>) but that uses a huge power of your battery power &#x26; your phone will end up shutting down in a short period of time.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1080px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e3257747c85f8856fc4dc39f3c0cbc8a/243ce/nexus6p.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Nexus 6p\"\n        title=\"Nexus 6p\"\n        src=\"/static/e3257747c85f8856fc4dc39f3c0cbc8a/b4133/nexus6p.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e3257747c85f8856fc4dc39f3c0cbc8a/d5225/nexus6p.jpg 270w,\n/static/e3257747c85f8856fc4dc39f3c0cbc8a/3c312/nexus6p.jpg 540w,\n/static/e3257747c85f8856fc4dc39f3c0cbc8a/b4133/nexus6p.jpg 1080w,\n/static/e3257747c85f8856fc4dc39f3c0cbc8a/266b5/nexus6p.jpg 1620w,\n/static/e3257747c85f8856fc4dc39f3c0cbc8a/0bf41/nexus6p.jpg 2160w,\n/static/e3257747c85f8856fc4dc39f3c0cbc8a/243ce/nexus6p.jpg 4032w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"build-quality\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#build-quality\" aria-label=\"build quality permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Build quality</h2>\n<p>The build quality is good but keep in mind that itâ€™s a big phone that you will need two hands to use otherwise your hand will eventually get tired of using it and it hardly fits in your pocket ðŸ˜….</p>\n<h2 id=\"battery\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#battery\" aria-label=\"battery permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Battery</h2>\n<p>One of the main reasons I donâ€™t recommend buying this phone, it has battery issues which you will notice after few months of using the phone, the most frustrating thing is when it shuts down at 20% which gets really annoying over time.</p>\n<h2 id=\"performance\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#performance\" aria-label=\"performance permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Performance</h2>\n<p>Since itâ€™s rocking the stack android, you can delete the default apps if you donâ€™t use them and the user experience is nice &#x26; never gets slow while using it, the phone gets really hot though when youâ€™re watching a long video or playing some games that require huge computational work.</p>\n<h2 id=\"display\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#display\" aria-label=\"display permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Display</h2>\n<p>The display is a 2k LED screen with huge bezels on all sides with large ones on top &#x26; bottom.</p>\n<p>Enough with the Nexus 6p for now and letâ€™s jump into the <a href=\"https://amzn.to/2NX1JXq\">Google Pixel 2</a> now which most of my <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/smakosh19/\">Instagram</a> community has voted more for its review.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Keep in mind that Iâ€™m reviewing the Pixel 2 and not the Pixel 2 XL.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1080px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/09a759c2900121b6f7a23aec2e543d7d/243ce/pixel2box.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Pixel 2\"\n        title=\"Pixel 2\"\n        src=\"/static/09a759c2900121b6f7a23aec2e543d7d/b4133/pixel2box.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/09a759c2900121b6f7a23aec2e543d7d/d5225/pixel2box.jpg 270w,\n/static/09a759c2900121b6f7a23aec2e543d7d/3c312/pixel2box.jpg 540w,\n/static/09a759c2900121b6f7a23aec2e543d7d/b4133/pixel2box.jpg 1080w,\n/static/09a759c2900121b6f7a23aec2e543d7d/266b5/pixel2box.jpg 1620w,\n/static/09a759c2900121b6f7a23aec2e543d7d/0bf41/pixel2box.jpg 2160w,\n/static/09a759c2900121b6f7a23aec2e543d7d/243ce/pixel2box.jpg 4032w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Iâ€™ve been using it for a couple of months so far and Iâ€™m really satisfied with my decision of purchasing it!</p>\n<h2 id=\"camera-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#camera-1\" aria-label=\"camera 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Camera</h2>\n<p>It does take amazing pictures, the portrait mode is epic and provides both the normal picture and the one with the blurring effect, it has the night sight mode that helps take good looking photos without the need to activate the flash.</p>\n<h2 id=\"portrait-mode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#portrait-mode\" aria-label=\"portrait mode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Portrait mode</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1080px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3d9359bfd8247436d77e37fab5682ad1/c2b56/portrait.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Portrait mode\"\n        title=\"Portrait mode\"\n        src=\"/static/3d9359bfd8247436d77e37fab5682ad1/b4133/portrait.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3d9359bfd8247436d77e37fab5682ad1/d5225/portrait.jpg 270w,\n/static/3d9359bfd8247436d77e37fab5682ad1/3c312/portrait.jpg 540w,\n/static/3d9359bfd8247436d77e37fab5682ad1/b4133/portrait.jpg 1080w,\n/static/3d9359bfd8247436d77e37fab5682ad1/266b5/portrait.jpg 1620w,\n/static/3d9359bfd8247436d77e37fab5682ad1/0bf41/portrait.jpg 2160w,\n/static/3d9359bfd8247436d77e37fab5682ad1/c2b56/portrait.jpg 3024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"night-sight\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#night-sight\" aria-label=\"night sight permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Night sight</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1080px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/065dc9c39da723a1caa80f345fe86462/243ce/sight.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        