jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"DBrand dragon skin\"\n        title=\"DBrand dragon skin\"\n        src=\"/static/4372dcbffa47f4eca2ec71f8165d2d82/b4133/dragon.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4372dcbffa47f4eca2ec71f8165d2d82/d5225/dragon.jpg 270w,\n/static/4372dcbffa47f4eca2ec71f8165d2d82/3c312/dragon.jpg 540w,\n/static/4372dcbffa47f4eca2ec71f8165d2d82/b4133/dragon.jpg 1080w,\n/static/4372dcbffa47f4eca2ec71f8165d2d82/266b5/dragon.jpg 1620w,\n/static/4372dcbffa47f4eca2ec71f8165d2d82/0bf41/dragon.jpg 2160w,\n/static/4372dcbffa47f4eca2ec71f8165d2d82/243ce/dragon.jpg 4032w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"battery-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#battery-1\" aria-label=\"battery 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Battery</h2>\n<p>Has a 2700mAh battery that works really well and holds for a day of use while:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>taking pictures</li>\n<li>listening to music with bluetooth enabled</li>\n<li>Data usage enabled</li>\n<li>Instagram, Twitter, Telegram etcâ€¦</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"performance-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#performance-1\" aria-label=\"performance 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Performance</h2>\n<p>Doesnâ€™t get hot at all even after using it for a long period of time, supports and works fine with the Google Daydream VR headset.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1080px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/751eadd09a0cb1f2267c9bcb62c0a056/a421d/vr.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.31887201735358%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Google Daydream VR headset\"\n        title=\"Google Daydream VR headset\"\n        src=\"/static/751eadd09a0cb1f2267c9bcb62c0a056/b4133/vr.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/751eadd09a0cb1f2267c9bcb62c0a056/d5225/vr.jpg 270w,\n/static/751eadd09a0cb1f2267c9bcb62c0a056/3c312/vr.jpg 540w,\n/static/751eadd09a0cb1f2267c9bcb62c0a056/b4133/vr.jpg 1080w,\n/static/751eadd09a0cb1f2267c9bcb62c0a056/266b5/vr.jpg 1620w,\n/static/751eadd09a0cb1f2267c9bcb62c0a056/0bf41/vr.jpg 2160w,\n/static/751eadd09a0cb1f2267c9bcb62c0a056/a421d/vr.jpg 2305w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"display-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#display-1\" aria-label=\"display 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Display</h2>\n<p>Itâ€™s an AMOLED display with a full hd screen resolution.</p>\n<h2 id=\"bonus\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#bonus\" aria-label=\"bonus permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Bonus</h2>\n<p>Pixel 2 is water resistant, doesnâ€™t have an audio jack, has unlimited photo storage and will get upcoming Android updates.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Forgot to mention that both phones have a fingerprint sensor on the rear.</p>\n</blockquote>","description":"Iâ€™ve been using the Nexus 6p for 2 years until recently as I had to upgrade to the Google Pixel 2 forâ€¦","ti